642
00:43:31,160 --> 00:43:32,785
You can count on that.

643
00:43:33,600 --> 00:43:34,986
[C.P. GRUNTING]

644
00:43:42,120 --> 00:43:43,949
[C.P. COUGHING]

645
00:43:47,480 --> 00:43:49,230
C.P.: Morning.

646
00:44:00,840 --> 00:44:02,146
